{"tid":419361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今天起，鉛水管正式從台北市消失","createTime":"2017-09-30T12:06:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T04:21:35.000Z","uid":31757,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a426b618fc50e2b409e594c70d3ab2232b9f8643","tid":419361,"uid":31757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T12:06:31.000Z","msg":"今天起，鉛水管正式從台北市消失。<br />\n鉛水管問題在2015年被揭露後，原先的計畫要花10年更換，但這顯然不合民眾期望。在謝維洲議員的提案監督下，台北市自來水事業處重訂計畫，在3年內斥資20億元，加速汰換台北市內1.7萬戶鉛管。<br />\n結果不到2年時間，比預定的期限早15個月，台北市鉛水管已全數汰換完成，這都要歸功北水處員工的努力，以及區長、里長的居間協調，很多位在防火巷內的鉛管，施工困難，連要溝通施工都很困難，但最後都能一一克服。<br />\n這種看不見的改變，人民無感，對選票沒有幫助，但政治應該落實在每天的生活之中，該做的還是要做。感謝同仁們面對問題、解決問題，這個幾十年的問題終於解決了，市民朋友從今天起，再也不用擔心喝到鉛水。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/DoctorKoWJ/posts/1132790500156262\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDoctorKoWJ%2Fposts%2F1132790500156262&d=S4zWsKm%2BY%2Fb0UDJCxtvU4r%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=1e849c36\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/DoctorKoWJ/posts/1132790500156262</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/200520_a9e7a0431ae44917a5824a556b3f68e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F200520_a9e7a0431ae44917a5824a556b3f68e9.jpg&h=c5316091&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"134abdec19ceb9f3f4a6bdc9c46666ab37d8baad","tid":419361,"uid":35248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T12:08:35.000Z","msg":"香港：鉛水有益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55bdf64b4c378699bd0f0045eff830d3bd4aab3e","tid":419361,"uid":39872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T12:14:00.000Z","msg":"焗腸：可以延年益壽"},{"pid":"03a4f25ad8d69fc497b39517295b1920850fee25","tid":419361,"uid":54452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T12:26:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今天起，鉛水管正式從台北市消失。<br />\n鉛水管問題在2015年被揭露後，原先的計畫要花10年更換，但這顯然不合民眾期望。在謝維洲議員的提案監督下，台北市自來水事業處重訂計畫，在3年內斥資20億元，加速汰換台北市內1.7萬戶鉛管。<br />\n結果不到2年時間，比預定的期限早15個月，台北市鉛水管已全數汰換完成，這都要歸功北水處員工的努力，以及區長、里長的居間協調，很多位在防火巷內的鉛管，施工困難，連要溝通施工都很困難，但最後都能一一克服。<br />\n這種看不見的改變，人民無感，對選票沒有幫助，但政治應該落實在每天的生活之中，該做的還是要做。感謝同仁們面對問題、解決問題，這個幾十年的問題終於解決了，市民朋友從今天起，再也不用擔心喝到鉛水。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/DoctorKoWJ/posts/1132790500156262\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDoctorKoWJ%2Fposts%2F1132790500156262&d=S4zWsKm%2BY%2Fb0UDJCxtvU4r%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=1e849c36\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/DoctorKoWJ/posts/1132790500156262</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/200520_a9e7a0431ae44917a5824a556b3f68e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F200520_a9e7a0431ae44917a5824a556b3f68e9.jpg&h=c5316091&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\nGoogle下都知&rdquo;鉛水喉&rdquo;係術語,正試名稱叫&rdquo;鍍鋅鐵喉&rdquo;...<br />\n含鉛嘅物料係好早就知對人體有害,而呢個禍害仲係會影響下一代，老早就blacklisted左。<br />\n台北人都係最緊要賺錢，你死你事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果真係咁無知，結論真係來生不做亜洲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77029fbc4f3032401d06be02abf48d6fb8ba687d","tid":419361,"uid":75694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T12:27:01.000Z","msg":"香港都少鉛管架<br />\n<br />\n但係接駁位同焊接出事呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6305cc7f5293d7d667be4d5c0f9ba9cfd6eb0fd3","tid":419361,"uid":31757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T14:55:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港都少鉛管架<br />\n<br />\n但係接駁位同焊接出事呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係態度問題 , 人地唔會話延年益壽跟住唔做野"},{"pid":"c62b45de799293a6056f788a3eea4ed185fe26d7","tid":419361,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T15:00:21.000Z","msg":"依啲 post 唔會有連登仔推架啦 <br />\n<br />\n因為佢地從來唔會面對"},{"pid":"ee6bd6d108b8c91556b417a630b3df0e91a443a0","tid":419361,"uid":54452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T03:10:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港都少鉛管架<br />\n<br />\n但係接駁位同焊接出事呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係態度問題 , 人地唔會話延年益壽跟住唔做野</blockquote><br />\n唔通同你講成個組件啲喉本身有問題，然候成棟拆左佢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769d91851bc5d49a6f1e6196a350a6ca4fe087e3","tid":419361,"uid":65547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T04:21:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n銅喉燒接駁位個陣落個物料含鉛先有鉛水<br />\n唔係鉛水喉事"}]}